{"word":"πείρω","slug":"πείρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n80362\" key=\"pei/rw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πείρω</orth>, <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">aor. 1</tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔπειρα</foreign>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <sense id=\"n80362.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πεῖρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:317\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.317</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc. :—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">pf.</tns> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πέπαρμαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:246\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.246</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc. : <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπάρην <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">[ᾰ]</pron> </foreign>(<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀνα-</etym>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:94\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.94</biblScope> </bibl> :—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pierce, run through</tr_>, mostly of cooking, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κρέα τ᾽ ὤπτων, ἄ